reviewText: It's a shame this was done like this,in the interviews with Freddie Mercury you either cannot hear what the interviewer is asking (it sounds muffled) or you hear some sort of flapping sound like a flag in the wind or it sounds like they are in a tin can also the picture is pretty blurred,most of the interviews are in Germany and one looks like it was done by a Hungarian local tv station or something, however the few bits you can hear properly are intetesting.
Not impressed, this looks like it was done in a basement by my younger brother. This is not how Freddy Mercury's memory should be saved...everything about it screams Dollar Store! !What a rip off!
